<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id62d1e074-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2008—<ref href="/us/pl/110/411">Pub. L. 110–411</ref> substituted “2009 through 2013” for “1997 through 2007”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—<ref href="/us/pl/107/292">Pub. L. 107–292</ref> substituted “1997 through 2007” for “1997, 1998, 1999, 2000, and 2001”.</p>
</note>
