<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id62d1e076-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1996-10-26">Oct. 26, 1996</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/330/s705">section 705 of Pub. L. 104–330</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s4211">section 4211 of this title</ref>.</p>
